cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.CE, cs.AI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on natural language processing techniques to represent discharge summaries. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses machine learning classifiers to construct predictive models. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is a possible category as the paper discusses the potential benefits of early recognition of ICU readmission in terms of lowering treatment cost and improving patient outcomes. 
- cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) is another possible category as the paper applies machine learning techniques to healthcare data. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper uses machine learning techniques to predict ICU readmission risk.
